{
  "stem": "9168.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the three months went to another three months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Fortunately, she had that farm in Kansas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And after 13 months, I passed my-- my high speed test at 200 words per minute, which was the graduating.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two years-- it was a two-year course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I have a very good friend, even to this day, a court reporter in Omaha, Nebraska, who was in the school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went in, and he was there quite a while after I left.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We laugh about that today.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He probably still wonders how you did it in 13 months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was-- you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had three job offers immediately-- one in Chicago, and one in Sioux Falls, South Dakota, and one in Detroit.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew after traveling in those snow blizzards down the canyons in downtown Chicago, that I did not want to work there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought about how nice it would be-- Sioux Falls, South Dakota.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I knew there was a military base there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I somehow had a negative feeling about like, military bases and-- and going to work there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I went to Detroit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I really don't know, unless that was-- unless it was through publicity in the paper, maybe, about GIs and-- and the-- I-- I don't remember anything particularly negative.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was a-- it was a GI town, and I wasn't sure that's where I wanted to be.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I took a job with a freelance court reporting agency there, meaning that we worked in-- on assignment in the court-- courts of Detroit-- in taking depositions, which were eventually used in court proceedings; reporting conventions, such as a Bar Association convention.",
      "word_count": 42
    }
  ],
